---
title: 'Produktside'
description: ''
order: 4
bodyClass: ''
tags: ['template']
---
{% extends 'base.njk' %}

{%- from "macros/button.njk" import button -%}
{%- from "macros/microcard.njk" import microcard -%}

{% block content %}
  <main class="py-8 text-lg md:py-12 px-clamp-gap">
    <div class="relative max-w-screen-lg mx-auto grid sm:grid-cols-[6rem_auto] gap-x-8 items-start mb-12">
      {{ '/src/_includes/svg/pictograms/utvidet-barnetrygd.svg' | svgContents('w-[calc(8vw+3rem)] h-auto max-w-24 md:-ml-2 text-green-800 absolute right-0 top-3 sm:static') | safe }}

      <div class="sm:col-start-2 sm:row-start-1">
        <p class="text-base tracking-wider uppercase opacity-70">Pengestøtte</p>
        <h1 class="min-w-0 pr-24 mt-1 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:pr-0 sm:text-5xl sm:leading-tight">Utvidet barnetrygd</h1>
        <p class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-5 text-base opacity-70">
          Oppdatert 22. desember 2022
        </p>
      </div>

      {# Intro #}
      <div class="sm:col-start-2 grid md:grid-cols-[2.1fr_0.9fr] gap-x-16 items-start gap-4 mt-8">
        <div class="markdown">
          <p>Du kan få utvidet barnetrygd når du bor alene med barn under 18 år. Dette er barnetrygd for et barn mer enn du faktisk bor sammen med.</p>

          <p>Du kan også få småbarnstillegg. Dette er et tillegg til utvidet barnetrygd for enslige forsørgere som har barn mellom 0 og 3 år, og som også mottar full overgangsstønad.</p>
        </div>

        {# Innholdsfortegnelse #}
        <div class="w-full max-w-3xl mt-6 md:sticky md:col-start-2 md:top-4 md:row-span-2 md:mx-0 md:max-w-none md:-mt-1.5 md:pl-6 md:border-l md:border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Innhold</h2>
          {% set index = sections.slice(1) %}
          <ul class="pt-1">
            {% for item in index %}
              <li class="py-1.5 text-xl"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#{{ item.title | slugify }}">{{ item.title }}</a></li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Nyttig å vite</h2>
          <ul class="pt-1">
            <li class="py-1.5 text-xl"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Klagerettigheter</a></li>
            <li class="py-1.5 text-xl"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Lov om barnetrygd</a></li>
            <li class="py-1.5 text-xl"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Pensjonsopptjening for omsorgsarbeid</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {# Filter + Innhold #}
        <div class="grid w-full max-w-3xl gap-4 md:row-start-2 md:mx-0 md:max-w-none">

          {# Filter #}
          <div class="px-6 py-4 mt-4 sm:px-8 sm:py-6 bg-blue-50 max-w-prose">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Hva er situasjonen din</h2>
            <p>Fortell oss litt om situasjonen din, så viser vi bare den informasjonen som er relevant for deg.</p>

            <button class="flex items-center justify-between w-full gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 mt-4 bg-white border-b-2 border-gray-400 md:max-w-max" type="button">
              <span>Tilpass innholdet</span>
              {{ '/src/_includes/svg/icons/chevron-down.svg' | svgContents('w-4 h-4') | safe }}
            </button>
          </div>

          {# Innhold #}
          {% for section in sections %}
            {% if not loop.first %}
            <div class="relative p-6 grid bg-gray-50 rounded max-w-prose min-w-0 sm:p-8 {{ 'mt-12 pt-8 sm:pt-12' if section.icon }}" id="{{ section.title | slugify }}">
              {% if section.icon %}
              <div class="absolute top-0 inline-grid p-4 mx-auto -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-green-200 rounded-full left-1/2 justify-self-center">
                {{ section.icon | svgContents('w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7') | safe }}
              </div>
              {% endif %}

              <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl sm:leading-snug {{ 'md:-mt-2' if section.icon }}">{{ section.title | safe }}</h2>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 mb-8 text-base text-blue-500 hover:underline hover:text-blue-600">
                {{ '/src/_includes/svg/icons/link.svg' | svgContents('w-4 h-4') | safe }}
                <span>Kopier lenke</span>
              </a>
              <div class="markdown">
              {% for block in section.contentBlocks %}
                {% if block.type === 'markdown' %}
                  <div class="markdown">
                    {{ block.data  | markdown | safe }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.type === 'actions' %}
                <div class="grid gap-1.5 sm:flex">
                  {% for item in block.data %}
                    {{ button(
                      {
                        text: item.text,
                        href: '#',
                        variant: item.variant
                      }
                    ) }}
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.type === 'microcards' %}
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">{{ block.title | safe }}</h4>
                  <div class="flex mt-1 flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                    {% for item in block.data %}
                      {{ microcard(item) }}
                    {% endfor %}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.type === 'tiles' %}
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">{{ block.title | safe }}</h4>
                  <div class="grid gap-3 mt-1">
                    {% for item in block.data %}
                      <div class="relative flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow hover:z-10 transition-colors duration-200 ease-out {{ item.hover }} ring-1 ring-gray-500/5">
                        {{ item.icon | svgContents('max-w-16 h-auto w-[calc(8vw+1rem)]') | safe }}
                        <a class="flex-1 text-xl font-semibold leading-snug after:absolute after:inset-0" href="#">{{ item.title }}</a>
                      </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.type === 'line' %}
                  <hr class="border-deepblue-100" />
                {% endif %}

              {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
{% endblock %}
